  # How I Learned to Prompt Claude Code Better — Four Modes
  
  [![Stéphane Derosiaux](https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fill:32:32/1*UZJiZsa2WIQGqSHgN6jtYw.jpeg)](https://sderosiaux.medium.com/?source=post_page---byline--177bddcfa6bd---------------------------------------)
  
